OL,3,CHSE leads investigation into death of
OL,4,CEverton fan Michael Jones
OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive is now
OL,7,Fleading the investigation into the
OL,8,Fdeath of an fan who was working on the
OL,9,Fclub's new stadium.
OL,11,FVentilation engineer Michael Jones,
OL,12,Ffrom , died on 14 August 2023 after
OL,13,Fbeing injured at Bramley-Moore Dock in
OL,14,F, where Everton's new ground is being
OL,15,Fbuilt.
OL,17,FAn inquest heard Michael, who was 26,
OL,18,Fsuffered severe head injuries when he
OL,19,Fwas caught between a beam and a piece
OL,20,Fof machinery.
