OL,4,CEverton fan Michael Jones
OL,6,FThe court was told Mr Jones, whose
OL,7,Fmiddle name was Goodison, had been
OL,8,Fwearing a hard hat, which was damaged
OL,9,Fin the incident.
OL,11,FSenior coroner Andrew Rebello said
OL,12,Fthis was a "very complex and technical
OL,13,Finvestigation" and the inquest was
OL,14,Fadjourned until 29 February.
OL,16,FMichael Jones was employed by Mersey
OL,17,FVent Ltd, and the stadium contractor,
OL,18,FLaing O'Rourke, will be asked to
OL,19,Fparticipate in the inquest.
