OL,3,CHSE leads investigation into death of
OL,4,CEverton fan Michael Jones
OL,6,FHSE inspector John Padfield said: "We
OL,7,Fhave been a part of this inquiry from
OL,8,Fthe outset and we will continue to
OL,9,Fthoroughly investigate Michael's
OL,10,Ftragic death as the lead agency
OL,12,F"This will aim to establish if there
OL,13,Fhave been any breaches of health and
OL,14,Fsafety law.
OL,16,F"We are in regular contact with
OL,17,FMichael's family and our thoughts
OL,18,Fremain with them at this time."
