OL,4,CEverton fan Michael Jones
OL,6,FFollowing Mr Jones' death, his family
OL,7,Fdescribed him as a "beloved son,
OL,8,Fbrother, uncle and friend".
OL,10,FThey said: "He was a lifelong Blue who
OL,11,Fwas so happy to be working on the new
OL,12,Fstadium.
OL,14,F"We want to thank the NHS staff and
OL,15,Fwork colleagues who did their best for
OL,16,FMichael.
OL,18,F"He will be missed beyond words."
